Europe map, start of 1941

Eric Rauchway

7/16/2022

Map draws from Natural Earth datasets and also from Michael de Groot’s “Building the New Order” as well as the Rand-McNally map of Africa in 1939, from the David Rumsey Map Collection. Information on the targets of the Blitz to the end of 1940 from Basil Collier, The Defence of the United Kingdom. Color palette adapted from CARTOcolors. Made using R with ggplot and sf, as well as some use of QGIS. With gratitude especially to Kieran Healy.
